<section id="To_access_Usage_data" remap="TID_15477">
	<title>Accessing Usage Data</title>
	<para />
	<procedure>
		<title>To Access Usage Data</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Cloud Intelligence</guimenu><guisubmenu>Usage</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In the <guilabel>Options</guilabel> area, select a <guilabel>Date</guilabel>. More choices will display.
			</para>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="images/2307.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</step>
		<step>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						From <guilabel>Period</guilabel>, select either <guimenuitem>Day</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Hour</guimenuitem>. If you select <guimenuitem>Hour</guimenuitem>, you will be prompted for which hour in UTC time.
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						From <guilabel>Category</guilabel>, select the category for the tag.
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						From <guilabel>Entry</guilabel>, select the tag from within the category that you want usage data for.
					</para>
				</listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>